[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 2.3"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 2.3 are now fixed in Tails 2.4.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to Tails 2.4|news/version_2.4]] as soon as possible.

